1484703283.text: "Cytochrome c release, caspase-3-(-like) protease activation, and apoptosis induced by antitumor drugs were accelerated by overexpression of Bcl-2 lacking a Bcl-2 homology (BH) 1 domain (Bcl-2 / DeltaBH1), but not by that of BH2, BH3, or BH4 domain deleted Bcl-2."
